{"tid":624987,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"【中環老店】新香園將於月底結業","createTime":"2018-04-11T05:39:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-12T02:48:36.000Z","uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e2828b2d54a96be2ffee020708c04f925adff7ac","tid":624987,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T05:39:13.000Z","msg":"「新香園」在中環已有二十多年歷史，這是一間後巷內的早餐小店，開朝六至下午五時。小店並非有名氣日賣幾千杯奶茶的名店，裝修亦簡陋，老闆低調較少接受採訪，亦沒有花費做宣傳，由招呼一眾熟客起家，每逢早餐與午餐時段也人來人往，客人定時走入巷中覓食，成為中環上班族的隱蔽早午餐熱點。<br />\n<br />\n可惜，店舖已對外宣佈於4月27日正式結業，相信很多熟客亦大感不捨。老闆曾在訪問時談及絕不賣舖，記者致電店舖詢問有關結業情況，店員稱結業與鄰近的大廈收購有關，不得不結業，年屆60多歲的老闆亦不打算另尋新店重開，選擇光榮退休。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180410/large/1523353517_7332.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180410%2Flarge%2F1523353517_7332.jpg&h=2f788efa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/realtime/article/20180410/58056511\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180410%2F58056511&d=a3%2FA6laLgyZZ0mbNJ%2FLrwhFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=f6720aba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180410%2F58056511&h=ee97b190\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/realtime/article/20180410/58056511</a></div>"},{"pid":"374e4d2bcdc68244095c9728fd00213a97f04012","tid":624987,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T05:41:36.000Z","msg":"光顧小店的客人十居其九點香滑奶茶，沙爹牛肉和沙薑雞翼，餐牌價錢在中環區來說相當相宜，30多元一個餐，全部麵食用出前一丁，秘製沙爹醬味令人垂涎，醬汁帶少少辛口，還夾雜着微微的花生碎粒，相當出色。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180410/large/1523353521_3763.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180410%2Flarge%2F1523353521_3763.jpg&h=ccf3e2d5&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n精心調製的一杯奶茶，是不少人早上不可缺少的飲品，令人精神為之一振，中環的老牌茶檔，如果想一嚐箇中味道，不妨於結業前再去一次。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180410/large/1523353523_c6fb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180410%2Flarge%2F1523353523_c6fb.jpg&h=d00d53aa&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"91678483669c699e39f998fc78b37847e1e78652","tid":624987,"uid":54524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T01:33:14.000Z","msg":"係咪真係好食？"},{"pid":"49fd16cccb83eb9cbeaf2abe908e0d606d5e9747","tid":624987,"uid":17641,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T02:14:16.000Z","msg":"廿幾年叫老店？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b7e67ef73a87a7966279dd88f05066022ceac5c","tid":624987,"uid":1096,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T02:18:52.000Z","msg":"等睇比財團買咗個名，又再開返"},{"pid":"cdf390190d485fbe0d3f6e5cdafb606c43a30fec","tid":624987,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T02:48:36.000Z","msg":"送舊迎新"}]}